==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Scattering
<hw>Scat"ter*ing</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Going or falling in various
directions; not united or aggregated; divided among many; <as>as,
<ex>scattering</ex> votes</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Scattering</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Scattering
<hw>Scat"ter*ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Act of strewing about;
something scattered.</def> <rj><au>South.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Scatteringly</ent>⟦br⟧
